Elame index ah ans varum
Index col ku mtm thaniya ..oru table maintain panum...in order and uses b tree....apo dhn fast ah retrieve pana mudiyum
B tree la epdi search nadakum. Na...
If the tree oda order vanthu 3 or greater than 3 means....

K nary search panum 

Ipo kamina binary search panum...in T(logn) time ila...
B tree is a self balancing tree  data structure
Binary tree  must have at most 2 child per node
B tree can have multiple values
Athu ascending order la... sort pani... table maintain panum...
So, that retrieve easy ah irkum...
